{"QUACK":[{"def":"To utter a sound like the cry of a duck.","pos":""},{"def":"To make vain and loud pretensions; to boast.","pos":""}],"QUACK GRASS":[{"def":"See Quitch grass.","pos":""}],"QUACKERY":[{"def":"The acts, arts, or boastful pretensions of a quack; false pretensions to any art; empiricism.","pos":""}],"QUACKISH":[{"def":"Like a quack; boasting; characterized by quackery.","pos":""}],"QUACKLE":[{"def":"To suffocate; to choke.","pos":""}],"QUACKSALVER":[{"def":"One who boasts of his skill in medicines and salves, or of the efficacy of his prescriptions; a charlatan; a quack; a mountebank.","pos":""},{"def":"Evil; bad; baffling; as, a quade wind.","pos":""}]}